  "notes": [
    "This paper demonstrates a novel mechanism where PSMD14 drives lung adenocarcinoma progression through dual pathway activation (TGF-\u03b2/Smad and PI3K/AKT/mTOR) via HMMR stabilization through K63-linked deubiquitination.",
    "The study provides evidence for combination therapy using PSMD14 inhibitor Capzimin with TGF-\u03b2 inhibitor galunisertib as a potential treatment strategy.",
    "PSMD14 shows excellent diagnostic performance (AUC = 0.898) and strong prognostic value across multiple survival endpoints in lung adenocarcinoma."
  ]
